headline: Why Super Micro Computer Stock Is Plummeting This Week
summary: Super Micro Computer issued updated guidance for fiscal Q3 this week, and investors weren't happy with the print.  Supermicro attributed the sales and earnings shortfall to customer orders being pushed further out.  Super Micro Computer (NASDAQ: SMCI) stock has seen big sell-offs this week.

headline: Is Super Micro Computer Stock a Buy Now?
summary: Super Micro Computer stock declined sharply after it cut Q3 sales and earnings guidance.  This company was once a high-flying hero of the early artificial intelligence (AI) boom, but shares of Super Micro Computer (NASDAQ: SMCI) have become the antagonist in investor portfolios.  Super Micro Computer continues to generate profitable growth, which keeps the potential open for shares to rebound.
